ificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Plan Your Visit</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6217338\">\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7137068\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7137068\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Around 30 sightseers behind railings at a scenic overlook with colorful peaks and cliffs in the background and a blanket of clouds overhead.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/mather-point-2021.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"mather point 2021\"/>\n<figcaption>Viewing Grand Canyon from Mather Point on the South Rim. NPS </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7001606\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7001606\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/grand-canyon-visitor-center.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2230772,grand-canyon-visitor-center.htm,11006|\">South Rim Visitor Center</a></strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Open daily from 9 am to 5 pm </strong>(December 7, 2025 - April 18, 2026)</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5920414\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5920414\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h3><span style=\"color:null;\">All visitors MUST have an entrance pass</span></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/fees.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6714073,/grca/planyourvisit/fees.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Learn about entrance fee costs and passes </a> &gt;</strong></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2681989\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2681989\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/0531fyp.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Two people behind a guardrail on the right looking at colorful peaks within Grand Canyon\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/0531fyp.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Viewing Grand Canyon from Mather Point on the South Rim </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">First Time to Visit?  </span></h2>\n<p><strong>I want to visit the...</strong><br/>\n<strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/placestogo.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1870413,placestogo.htm,11006|\">South Rim</a></strong> - open all year<br/>\n<br/>\n<strong><a href=\"/grca/northrimstatus.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=8060425,northrimstatus.htm,10957|\">North Rim</a></strong> - <strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">Closed -Current Status </span></strong><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/skywalk.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1961411,skywalk.htm,11006|\">Grand Canyon Skywalk</a> <br/>\n<br/>\n<strong>More about: <span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">--</span><em> </em><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/lodging.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1878476,lodging.htm,11006|\">Lodging</a></strong> <span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">—</span> <strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/camping.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2638417,camping.htm,11006|\">Camping</a></strong><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/backcountry.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1897982,backcountry.htm,11006|\">Backcountry Hiking</a> <span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">——</span> <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/whitewater-rafting.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1906896,whitewater-rafting.htm,11006|\">River Trips</a></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5195890\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5195890\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Yaki-5197.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"From a limestone ledge, looking out across the landscape as the last light of day illuminates peaks and ridgelines.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Yaki-5197.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"Yaki Point at Sunset\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>View from Yaki Point on the South Rim </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/basicinfo.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2627713,basicinfo.htm,11006|\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Basic Information</span></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/hours.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1870396,hours.htm,11006|\">Operating Hours and Seasons</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/fees.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6714073,/grca/planyourvisit/fees.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Fees and Passes</a> <span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">——</span> <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/permitsandreservations.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2636706,permitsandreservations.htm,11006|\">Permits</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/webcams.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1927865,webcams.htm,14075|\">Webcams </a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/weather-condition.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1885198,weather-condition.htm,11006|\">Weather &amp; Road Conditions</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/sunrise_set_moon.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1968731,sunrise_set_moon.htm,11006|\">Sunrise &amp; Sunset Times  </a></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6089310\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6089310\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Traveling?</strong> Call <strong>928-638-7496</strong> for recorded information about current park road conditions and closures.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Visiting Grand Canyon with your pet? </strong> <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/pets.htm\">Things to know</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5089577\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5089577\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/P1490311-copy.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"from under the roof of an open air bus shelter, several people are about to board a white and green bus\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/P1490311-copy.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"P1490311 copy Village Loop bus stop at Yavapai Lodge. 2023 05 06 M. Quinn\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Visitors boarding a the Village (Blue) Route shuttle bus at Yavapai Lodge. </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/directions.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1869347,directions.htm,11006|\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Directions &amp; Transportation</span></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/maps.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1869356,maps.htm,11006|\">Park Maps</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/directions_s_rim.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1964482,directions_s_rim.htm,11006|\">Directions to South Rim</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/parking_sr.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1978773,/grca/planyourvisit/parking_sr.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">South Rim Parking</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/shuttle-buses.htm\">Free South Rim Shuttle Buses</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<strong><a href=\"/grca/northrimstatus.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=8060425,northrimstatus.htm,10957|\">North Rim</a></strong> - <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong>Current Status and Closures</strong></span> </p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5089611\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5089611\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/BAL_8986_2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"a number of people in front of historic Bright Angel Lodge in rustic style constructed of logs and stone. Yellow fall foliage.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/BAL_8986_2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Bright Angel Lodge on the South Rim </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/eatingsleeping.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2638076,eatingsleeping.htm,11006|\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Eating &amp; Sleeping</span></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/lodging.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1878476,lodging.htm,11006|\">Lodging</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/restaurants.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1878498,restaurants.htm,11006|\">Restaurants &amp; Groceries</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/camping.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2638417,camping.htm,11006|\">Camping Overview</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/cg-sr.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1954247,cg-sr.htm,11006|\">South Rim Camping</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<strong><a href=\"/grca/northrimstatus.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=8060425,northrimstatus.htm,10957|\">North Rim</a></strong> - <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">Lodging and Camping</span> <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong>CLOSED for the season</strong> </span></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5089635\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5089635\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/wt-390x220_2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Looking across the vast expanse of Grand Canyon landscape towards a round, stone Watchtower on the far right, perched on the edge of a cliff.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/wt-390x220_2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Desert View Watchtower, on the South Rim, near the east entrance to the park. </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/placestogo.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1870413,placestogo.htm,11006|\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Places To Go</span></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/historic-village.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6265783,historic-village.htm,14076|\">Historic South Rim Village</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/hermit-road.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5899888,/grca/planyourvisit/hermit-road.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Scenic Hermit Road - Free Shuttle Access</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/desert-view-drive.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2205910,desert-view-drive.htm,11006|\">Scenic Desert View Drive </a>(State Route 64)<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/desert-view.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=837948,desert-view.htm,11006|\">Desert View</a> at the East Entrance to the park<br/>\n<br/>\n<strong><a href=\"/grca/northrimstatus.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=8060425,northrimstatus.htm,10957|\">North Rim</a></strong> - <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><strong>Current Status and Closures</strong></span> </p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5089644\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5089644\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Watching_Sunset_03.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Two bicyclists along with several other people in silhouette are watching sunset at Grand Canyon\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Watching_Sunset_03.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"Watching Sunset 3\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Experiencing sunset from Hopi Point on the South Rim </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/things2do.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1829735,things2do.htm,11006|\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Things To Do</span></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/ranger-program.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1902706,/grca/planyourvisit/ranger-program.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Ranger Programs</a> <br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/visitorcenters.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1870415,/grca/planyourvisit/visitorcenters.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Visitor Centers</a> <br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/backcountry.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1897982,backcountry.htm,11006|\">Hiking</a> <span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">—</span> <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/mule_trips.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1968473,mule_trips.htm,11006|\">Mule Trips</a> <span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">—</span> <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/whitewater-rafting.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1906896,whitewater-rafting.htm,11006|\">Whitewater Rafting</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/bicycling.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2121386,bicycling.htm,11006|\">Bicycling</a> <span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">—</span> <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/guidedtours.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1962717,guidedtours.htm,11006|\">Guided Tours</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/sunrise_set_moon.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1968731,sunrise_set_moon.htm,11006|\">Sunrise and Sunset Times</a></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5089835\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5089835\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/calendar.htm\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Park Calendar of Events and Activities</span></a></h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h4><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/safety.htm\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Safety Information</span></a></h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h4><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/accessibility.htm\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Accessibility Guide</span></a></h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h4><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/lost-found.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1918496,lost-found.htm,11006|\"><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\">Lost and Found Property</span></a><span style=\"color:#3300cc;\"> </span><br/>\n</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7137019\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7137019\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/iPhone-mobile-app-200.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"three mobile phones side-by-side, are displaying screens from the NPS mobile app; the menu, map, and search.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/iPhone-mobile-app-200.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"iPhone mobile app promo 200\"/>\n</picture>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<p>The <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/app.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6332607,app.htm,11006|\">National Park Service Mobile App</a> is a great tool for <strong>planning your trip</strong>, then it can be used as a guide during your visit. You can <strong>download the maps</strong> and content from Grand Canyon National Park for offline use. It’s especially handy if you’re exploring remote areas or concerned about data limits. <strong>Free and available now.</strong><br/>\n<br/>\n<em><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/grand-canyon-national-park-public-health-update.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6397341,/grca/planyourvisit/grand-canyon-national-park-public-health-update.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Visit this webpage</a><span style=\"color:null;\"><strong> (updated daily) for the current list of what is open and closed, and the hours of operation. </strong></span></em></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6075416\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6075416\"> \n\n<div class=\"VideoHero\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\">\n<meta content=\"More Than A View - Grand Canyon In Depth - Episode 01\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content='In \"More Than A View,\" Park Ranger Stephanie Sutton invites us to go beyond the rim and explore all that Grand Canyon National Park has to offer; diverse life zones, landforms, and cultural history.' itemprop=\"description\"/>\n<meta content=\"T8M39S\" itemprop=\"duration\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E2F42EE6-155D-451F-6795C7769CD934F1/grca-grcaindepth01_splash.jpg\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/media/video/view.htm?id=E2F42EE6-155D-451F-6795C7769CD934F1\" itemprop=\"embedURL\"/>\n<meta content=\"2020-10-14 00:00:00.0\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/>\n<div class=\"VideoHero-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-big-play-centered vjs-16-9\" controls=\"\" height=\"264\" id=\"av_E2F42EE6155D451F6795C7769CD934F1\" poster=\"/common/uploads/imr/park/grca/BF1E41FE-155D-451F-67788889D254186F/BF1E41FE-155D-451F-67788889D254186F-large.jpg\" preload=\"metadata\" width=\"640\">\n<source label=\"720p\" res=\"720\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E2F42EE6-155D-451F-6795C7769CD934F1/grca-grcaindepth01_1280x720.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n<source label=\"480p\" res=\"480\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E2F42EE6-155D-451F-6795C7769CD934F1/grca-grcaindepth01_854x480.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n<source label=\"360p\" res=\"360\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E2F42EE6-155D-451F-6795C7769CD934F1/grca-grcaindepth01_640x360.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n<source label=\"240p\" res=\"240\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E2F42EE6-155D-451F-6795C7769CD934F1/grca-grcaindepth01_426x240.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n<track kind=\"captions\" label=\"English\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/closed-caption/imr/avElement/grca-GCID01MoreThan.vtt\" srclang=\"en\"/>\n</source></source></source></source></video>\n<button aria-disabled=\"false\" aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"vjs-embed-control vjs-button\" data-bs-target=\"#av_E2F42EE6155D451F6795C7769CD934F1EmbedModal\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" id=\"av_E2F42EE6155D451F6795C7769CD934F1EmbedButton\" title=\"Embed Video\" type=\"button\">Embed</button>\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"av_E2F42EE6155D451F6795C7769CD934F1EmbedModalLabel\" class=\"modal fade VideoJSEmbedModal\" id=\"av_E2F42EE6155D451F6795C7769CD934F1EmbedModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h1 class=\"modal-title\" id=\"av_E2F42EE6155D451F6795C7769CD934F1EmbedModalLabel\">\nEmbed Video\n</h1>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<textarea class=\"form-control\" id=\"av_E2F42EE6155D451F6795C7769CD934F1EmbedText\" rows=\"6\"></textarea>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"VideoHero-text\">\n<a class=\"VideoHero-videoLink visuallyhidden\" href=\"/media/video/keyboard-shortcuts.htm\">Visit our keyboard shortcuts docs for details</a>\n<dl class=\"result-details wrapped\">\n<dt>Duration:</dt><dd>8 minutes, 39 seconds</dd>\n</dl>\n<p itemprop=\"description\">In \"More Than A View,\" Park Ranger Stephanie Sutton invites us to go beyond the rim and explore all that Grand Canyon National Park has to offer; diverse life zones, landforms, and cultural history.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2439765\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2439765\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/family_4_1116_2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"family of 4 with 2 girls in between parents, grand canyon in background\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/family_4_1116_2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"\"/>\n</picture>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2>Traveling Green</h2>\nis a great way to help Grand Canyon and other areas you visit reduce carbon emissions, divert and reduce what goes into the waste stream, and to generally help the environment. Visit our <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/traveling-green.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2218455,traveling-green.htm,11006|\"><strong>Traveling Green</strong></a> page for helpful tips on planning your next green adventure.\n<p> </p>\n<p><em><strong style=\"color: #009900\">Thanks</strong></em> for doing what you can to help protect our environment!</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2621743\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2621743\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p><em>Grand Canyon National Park, in northern Arizona, encompasses 278 miles (447 km) of the Colorado River and adjacent uplands. Located on the ancestral homeland of <a href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/associated-tribes.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6277538,associated-tribes.htm,14076|\">11 Associated Tribes,</a> Grand Canyon is one of the most spectacular examples of erosion anywhere in the world—unmatched in the incomparable vistas it offers visitors on the rim. Grand Canyon National Park is a World Heritage Site. The National Park Service cares for the special places saved by the American people so that all may experience our heritage. <a href=\"/grca/learn/management/statistics.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1940428,statistics.htm,14084|\">Park Statistics</a></em></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1905736\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1905736\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<hr align=\"left\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"1\" title=\"\"/>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: February 27, 2026</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
